  "successionPatrimoineLegalSources": "• CC art. 457–640 — Diritto successorio\n• CC art. 470–471 — Riserve ereditarie\n• CC art. 498–504 — Forme del testamento\n• LPP art. 20 — Beneficiari del capitale LPP\n• OPP3 art. 2 — Beneficiari del pilastro 3a",
